name: Classy Makeup Brush Kit
description:
*The Classy Makeup Brush Kit is specially designed for a fun yet functional makeup application.  
*This set contains every brush needed to conquer the hottest makeup looks, from flawless and natural to the smokiest eye. 
*A versatile 18-piece brush set that comes in a beautiful quilted pouch and a pouch cover. The pouch is soft to the touch and will have you toting this collection with you everywhere.

This kit contains:
- Flat fan brush
- Powder brush 
- Angled blush brush
- Foundation brush 
- Buffing brush 
- Stippling brush 
- Big Concealer brush 
- Small Concealer brush 
- Allover shadow brush 
- Smudge brush 
- Blending brush 
- Crease brush 
- Smoky eye brush 
- Angled liner brush
- Angled eye brow brush
- Eye liner brush
- Lip brush
- Brow comb brush

description:

*Made of easy-to-clean durable synthetic material.

name: Travel Makeup Brush Kit
description:
Compact and cute, these miniature brushes can create a myriad of makeup looks. The shiny compact case protects the integrity of the bristles. Slip this set into your purse or travel bag for on-the-go fixes and easy, full-face application. 

This set contains:
- Powder Brush 
- Big Eye Shadow Brush 
- Small Eye Shadow Brush
- Angled Liner Brush 
- Lip Brush
- Sponge Tip Brush
- Brow Brush/Lash Comb

name: Compact Foundation Sponges
description:
*This two-pack of versatile sponges are the perfect addition to any makeup bag. 
*Use the light texture and soft sponge to achieve smooth, even coverage with your compact foundation or apply your favorite cream or powder products for a natural, mattified finish.

name: Powder Puff
description: *Specially designed to pick up and hold loose powder for an even application to all areas of the face.

name: Blending makeup sponge
description:
*Blending makeup sponge makes it easy to achieve complexion perfection. 
*The superb moisture retention of this tool makes it ideal for blending foundation, applying skincare products, and removing makeup imperfections. This sponge is washable and reusable.
*Use the rounded end of the sponge to cover large areas of the face and the pointed end to reach trickier spots and angles.

name: Classic Kabuki Brush
description:
*This kabuki brush made from the highest quality materials to achieve a flawless, airbrushed finish. 
*Sweep your favorite mineral makeup, loose powder, bronzer, and blush across the face with this Kabuki brush for smooth, full coverage. 
*Dense and extra soft, the domed shape adds a polish to all powder and pigment applications. 
*When used to buff in a circular motion, this multitasking tool leaves behind a beautiful, airbrushed finish on every last feature.

name: Retractable kabuki brush
description:
*The brush has the perfect bristle density for applying just the right amount of pigment for flawless, streak-free color.
**This medium-sized brush is an ideal travel companion. The retractable design keeps the brightly colored bristles protected and clean. 
*Remove the lid and push down on the protective black cylinder to expose the brush. When finished, gently lift up on the cylinder to retract the brush and replace the cap
*Perfect to toss in your bag and go.

name: Lip Brush
description:
*A synthetic-bristle lip brush that’s ideal for applying lipstick or gloss. 
*Defines the contours of the lip: applies fill quickly and easily. 
*This chic brush is equipped with a small, tapered point that allows you to easily swipe color and gloss " inside the lines." You can also use it to line the outer rims of your lips for extra definition.

name: Angled Eyeshadow Brush
description:
*This brush has soft, smooth fibers and a full, angled design.
*Soft and dense to shade or blend eye shadow or emollient-based products. This brush has soft, smooth fibers and a full, angled design.

name: All Over Eyeshadow Brush
description:
*For application of eye shadow to the lid area. This brush has a thick bundle of goat hair arranged in a rounded shape.
*The rounded tip makes it multi-purpose. Use it to cover your lower lid, shade your creases or highlight your brow bone.
*The all over eyeshadow brush can handle nearly every eyeshadow need, it's great for touchups and travel needs.

name: Eye Liner Brush
description:
*For precision lining of eye area or body detailing/design. 
*This brush has goat hair of just the right length and density for lining the eyes.

name: Classic Angled Liner Brush
description:
*This brush defines your lids with a thin line of color, it's the best bet for creating a dramatic cat-eye look.
*The nylon bristles allows you to use liquid, cream, and powder liners—wet or dry—with total control.

name: Classic Concealer Brush
description:
*A brush with firm, tapered bristles that make it easy to apply concealer and corrector on hard-to-reach areas, like the inner corners of your eyes and along the lash line. 
*The smooth, synthetic bristles of this concealer brush allows full, concentrated coverage that blends into skin flawlessly. 
*Besides ensuring seamless concealer application, it works it's magic with all cream products, including primer, eye cream, and cream shadow.

name: Big Concealer Brush
description:
*The smooth, synthetic bristles of this concealer brush allows full, concentrated coverage that blends into skin flawlessly. 
*Tightly packed hair and tapered edge fit contours of eyes and blemishes for complete coverage. 
*Besides ensuring seamless concealer application, it works it's magic with all cream products, including primer, eye cream, and cream shadow.

name: Foundation Brush
description:
*A tapered, chiseled brush designed to create a smooth, even finish, flawless look. Works well with liquid foundation.
*This tapered, chiseled brush fits the contours of your face and blends formulas seamlessly.

name: Small Duo Fibre Brush
description:
*Can be used with any formula colour- powder, fluid, cream or pigment. *The white, taklon bristles apply product and the black, goat bristles blend for flawless results—an ideal duo of natural and synthetic fibers. 
*Creates a controlled airbrush effect onto the skin.

name: Big Duo Fibre Brush
description:
*Can be used with powder, liquid or cream foundations.
*The white, taklon bristles apply product and the black, goat bristles blend for flawless results—an ideal duo of natural and synthetic fibers. 
*Creates an airbrush-like effect onto the skin.

name: Flat Buffing Brush
description:
*A large, flat-headed brush with very silky synthetic bristles
*Perfect for liquid, cream and powder foundation
*The specially designed flat shape promotes even coverage to the face and body without streaking for a beautiful finish on the face and body.

name: Angled Buffing brush
description:
*Silky synthetic bristles, perfect for liquid, cream or powder foundation
*The specially designed brush head is angled to fit the contours of the face

name: Classic Sculpting Brush- Angle Brush
description:
*Natural hair
*Specifically designed to be used for face contouring
*The bristles are ultra soft yet firm enough to enable the user to easily blend powder over the face

name: Classic Round Powder Brush
description:
*100% natural hair
*This full, round shape brush picks up powder foundations, setting, loose, bronzers, and blush distributes them for light to medium coverage
